  <brief_title>Addressing Heightened Levels of Aggression in Traumatized Offenders With Psychotherapeutic Means</brief_title>
  <official_title>Addressing Heightened Levels of Aggression in Traumatized Offenders With Psychotherapeutic Means: A Randomized Controlled Trial in Eastern DR Congo</official_title>
  <sponsors>
